window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Alex Hawk is still on Earth, but it is an earth with giant creatures and no technology.</b></p> <p>When he stepped through a mysterious, shimmering door in his basement, Alex found himself flung through time. Now, he is called upon to rescue the young girl who is thought to be the Chosen One - the savior of Kragdon-ah.</p> <p>A dangerous journey, new and deadlier creatures, and hairs-breadth escapes make <i>Lost in Kragdon-Ah </i>a worthy successor to <i>A Door into Time</i>.</p> <p>Includes a special note from the author.</p>"; 
